    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. The interior is nice and clean, and it runs like a dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or weekend adventures! I've kept up with the maintenance, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
