    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes a perfect balance between a spirited driver and a well-preserved classic. The exterior finish retains a deep, lustrous shine, complemented by clean alloy wheels and clear lens housings, though minor stone chips on the hood reflect its honest road history. Inside, the cabin remains a refined space; the leather upholstery is soft and free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronics, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is bone-dry and responds eagerly, backed by a comprehensive folder of service receipts. It has been recently fitted with a fresh set of performance tires and underwent a multi-point inspection to ensure it is turn-key ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this expertly maintained vehicle, which exemplifies a commitment to mechanical integrity and aesthetic preservation. Rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance, this motorcar offers a refined driving experience and remains in commendable condition throughout. It represents a sophisticated choice for those who demand reliability without compromise.",
      "price": 36450.0,
