    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been super well-loved? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s still in wonderful shape and ready for all your upcoming adventures! It runs smoothly, looks great, and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, so you can drive away feeling confident and happy. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
